      <div style="text-align: justify; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;">On November 14, 2022, SANUWAVE Health, Inc., a Nevada Corporation (the &#8220;Company&#8221;),
          issued a press release announcing its financial results for the third quarter ended September 30, 2022. As previously announced, a business update via conference call will occur on November 15, 2022, at 9:00 am EST. Materials are provided on the
          Company website </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">www.sanuwave.com/investors</span>.</span></div>

      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br />
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: justify; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">On August 14, 2022, the Company announced its financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2022.&#160; A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.2 to
        this Current Report on Form 8-K.</div>

      <div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;"> </span><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br />
        </span></div>

      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">The information in this Item 2.02 of this Current Report on Form 8-K and the exhibits attached hereto shall not be deemed to be &#8220;filed&#8221; for purposes of
        Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, and shall not be deemed incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended, except as shall be expressly set forth by specific reference in such
        filing.</div>

      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br />
      </div>

  <font style="font-size: 10pt;"> </font>
  <div>
    <hr noshade="noshade" align="center" style="height: 4px; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: none;"> </div>
  <div style="text-align: right;"> <font style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt;">Exhibit 99.1</font><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
    </font></div>
  <div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;" class="BRPFPageHeader">
      <div><br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div style="text-align: center;"><img height="121" width="468" src="image00002.jpg"></div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div><br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;">FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;">CONTACT:</div>
      <div style="text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Kevin Richardson, II</div>
      <div style="text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Chief Executive Officer</div>
      <div style="text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Investors@Sanuwave.com</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;">SANUWAVE Announces Q3 earnings</div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div><br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">EDEN PRARIE, MN, November 14, 2022 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- via NewMediaWire &#8211; SANUWAVE Health, Inc. (OTCPK: SNWV), a leading provider of next-generation
        FDA-approved wound care products, today announced 3<sup style="vertical-align: text-top; line-height: 1; font-size: smaller;">rd</sup> quarter results.</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">For the three-months and nine-months ended September 30, 2022:</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;" class="DSPFListTable" id="z607d46a99f1047b8a89a0c2ece46eba8">

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8226;</td>
            <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt;">
              <div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Revenues increased 12% to $4.2 million for the 3 months ended September 30, 2022, versus $3.7 million for the same period last year.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

      </table>
      <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;" class="DSPFListTable" id="z157f1b412ea1455ca745474f07875721">

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8226;</td>
            <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt;">
              <div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Revenue for the nine-months ended September 30, 2022, totaled approximately $11.2 million versus $8.7 million for the same period in the prior year, an increase of 28.5%.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

      </table>
      <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;" class="DSPFListTable" id="z7eb1a8bb1c794229a7ccfae2090be064">

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8226;</td>
            <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt;">
              <div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Gross margin also improved period over period to 85% from 58% a year ago and to 77% versus 58% for the nine-months ended September 30, 2022.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

      </table>
      <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;" class="DSPFListTable" id="z408994d29f504609ba2a291c8f54cdbf">

          <tr>
            <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8226;</td>
            <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; font-size: 10pt;">
              <div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Operating loss continued to decrease from the prior year.&#160; Operating loss for the three-months ended September 30, 2022, totaled $1.8 million as compared to the prior year at
                $3.4 million. Operating expense for the nine-months ended September 30, 2022, totaled $13.9 million, a decrease of 17.6% over the same period in the prior year.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>

      </table>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Mr. Kevin Richardson, CEO, stated, &#8220;We are very pleased with third quarter results which showed revenue growth year on year despite ongoing capacity
        constraints.&#160; Our focus is increasing sales at an accelerated rate as we ramp up capacity during the fourth quarter and into 2023.&#160; We have also decreased our operating expenses over the past year to a level where we can achieve profitable growth.&#8221;</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8220;As a result of our efforts to improve profitability and manage our expenses, the company is pleased to announce that it became EBITDA positive in the
        month of October and expects to continue this for Q4 as a whole.&#8221;</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;"> <br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">
      <div style="text-align: justify; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Subsequent to the end of the quarter, the company raised an additional approximately $2 million in order to maximize flexibility around sales hiring and inventory
        build.&#160; Terms were consistent with the August financing.&#160; This cash is not reflected in the Q3 statements.</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;"> <br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;">As previously announced a business update will occur via conference call on November 15,
          2022.&#160; Materials for the conference call at 9:00 a.m. EST are included on the company website, </font><font style="font-size: 10pt;"><u><font style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">www.sanuwave.com/investors</font></u><font style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">.</font></font></div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <font style="font-size: 10pt;"> </font>

    <div style="text-align: justify; color: #1D2228; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Telephone access is available by dialing the following numbers:</div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
    <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Conference ID: 13734492</div>

    <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">A replay will be available through November 29, 2022, shortly after conclusion of the event.</div>
    <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
    <div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;">About SANUWAVE</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">SANUWAVE Health is focused on the research, development, and commercialization of its patented, non-invasive and biological response-activating medical
        systems for the repair and regeneration of skin, musculoskeletal tissue, and vascular structures.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">SANUWAVE&#8217;s end-to-end wound care portfolio of regenerative medicine products and product candidates help restore the body&#8217;s normal healing processes.
        SANUWAVE applies and researches its patented energy transfer technologies in wound healing, orthopedic/spine, aesthetic/cosmetic, and cardiac/endovascular conditions.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;">Forward-Looking Statements</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: justify; color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-style: italic;">This press release may contain &#8220;forward-looking statements&#8221; within the meaning of the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act of
        1995, such as statements relating to financial results and plans for future business development activities and are thus prospective. Forward-looking statements include all statements that are not statements of historical fact regarding intent,
        belief or current expectations of the Company, its directors or its officers. Investors are cautioned that any such forward-looking statements are not guarantees of future performance and involve risks and uncertainties, many of which are beyond
        the Company&#8217;s ability to control. Actual results may differ materially from those projected in the forward-looking statements. Among the key risks, assumptions and factors that may affect operating results, performance and financial condition are
        risks associated with the regulatory approval and marketing of the Company&#8217;s product candidates and products, unproven pre-clinical and clinical development activities, regulatory oversight, the Company&#8217;s ability to manage its capital resource
        issues, competition, and the other factors discussed in detail in the Company&#8217;s periodic filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission. The Company undertakes no obligation to update any forward-looking statement.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>

              <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">-</td>
              <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt;">
                <div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Successfully completed MDSAP audit</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="z8d72f07971d3462ea57dc70307766b4d" class="DSPFListTable" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;">

            <tr>
              <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">-</td>
              <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt;">
                <div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Transitioned company from Suwanee GA to Eden Prairie MN</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="zf93a6234c6c3443f9f201f82fa473f99" class="DSPFListTable" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;">

            <tr>
              <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">-</td>
              <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt;">
                <div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Became current on SEC filings</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="zfa0c11a0a7264a15aaa1ffb3beca6003" class="DSPFListTable" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; width: 100%; text-align: left; color: #000000;">

            <tr>
              <td style="width: 18pt; font-size: 10pt;"><br>
              </td>
              <td style="width: 18pt; vertical-align: top; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">-</td>
              <td style="width: auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt;">
                <div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Launched Cosmetic and Orthopedics verticals with initial sales in each</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="text-align: left; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">&#8220;Our key ENERGY FIRST products, dermaPACE&#174; and UltraMIST&#174; continues to show strong acceptance and growth due to their robust clinical and financial
          profiles and increasingly attractive reimbursement, driven by a shift in payor focus to evidence based medicine in wound care..&#160; As our devices ship and our footprint widens, it has allowed the company to build a high degree of recurring usage
          revenue.&#160; This effort has been hampered over the past year as the company has also spent significant time, effort on fixing our accounting implementation that did not go as planned.&#160; Disruption from this process flow issue led to late filings,
          which led to our issues on the OTC and pink sheets. It also had a significant financial impact as it drew attention and resources away from growth.&#160; That is in the past and as we sit today, we are now timely and current in our SEC filings and the
          excessive outside costs to fix the problem have abated, lowering our break-even point.&#160; The company is now positioned to focus on profitable growth as we capture the opportunity in the wound care space,&#8221; stated Kevin Richardson, CEO.</div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      </div>
      <div class="BRPFPageBreakArea" style="clear: both; margin-top: 10pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;">
        <div class="BRPFPageBreak" style="page-break-after: always;">
          <hr noshade="noshade" style="margin: 4px 0px; width: 100%; border-width: 0; height: 2px; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; clear: both;"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="text-align: right; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-weight: bold;">Exhibit 99.2</font></div>
        <div style="text-align: right; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;"><font style="font-weight: bold;"> <br>
          </font></div>
        <div style="text-align: left; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;"><u>Quarter Financial Results</u></div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Revenues for the quarter, starting April 1, 2022 and ending <a name="z_Hlk37247980"></a>June 30, 2022, came in at $3.9 million. An increase of $1 million or 33% when
        compared to the $ 2.9 million for the same period in 2021.&#160; The increased revenue was primarily driven from an increase in sales of the UltraMIST system. The company moved manufacturing from Georgia to Minnesota which impacted timing of
        international shipments resulting in a $100,000 reduction in international revenue year-over-year.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Gross Margin increased to 72% from 64% as cost of revenue remained flat.&#160; The improvements were driven due to product mix and more efficient customer service and
        shipping.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">Operating loss was $2 million compared to $4 million in the year prior.&#160; The improvement is due to an increase in gross income and a reduction in sales, marketing, and
        R&amp;D expenses.</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: left; color: #333333; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;"><u>Conference Call</u></div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #0E101A;">SANUWAVE Health, Inc. will host a live conference call on Tuesday August 16, 2022, at 12:30
          (EDT)</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: rgb(29, 34, 40);"> to discuss recent business activity, provide an update on SEC filings, and detail strategic initiatives. </font><font style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A visual presentation accompaniment will be made available Tuesday morning via SANUWAVE&#8217;s website (https://sanuwave.com/about-us/news/).</font></div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 10pt;"><br>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold;">About SANUWAVE</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">SANUWAVE Health is focused on the research, development, and commercialization of its patented, non-invasive and biological response-activating medical systems for the
        repair and regeneration of skin, musculoskeletal tissue, and vascular structures.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>
      <div style="text-align: left; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10pt;">SANUWAVE&#8217;s ENERGY FIRST wound care portfolio consists of regenerative medicine products and product candidates help restore the body&#8217;s normal healing processes. SANUWAVE
        applies and researches its patented energy transfer technologies in wound healing, orthopedic/spine, aesthetic/cosmetic, and cardiac/endovascular conditions.</div>
      <div style="font-size: 10pt;">&#160;</div>

            <td valign="bottom" nowrap="nowrap" style="vertical-align: bottom; width: 52%; font-size: 10pt;">

<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="Show.toggleNext( this );">- Definition</a><div><p>Boolean flag that is true when the Form 8-K filing is intended to satisfy the filing obligation of the registrant as written communications pursuant to Rule 425 under the Securities Act.</p></div>
<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="Show.toggleNext( this );">+ References</a><div style="display: none;"><p>Reference 1: http://www.xbrl.org/2003/role/presentationRef<br> -Publisher SEC<br> -Name Securities Act<br> -Number 230<br> -Section 425<br></p></div>

e.removeAttribute('id');a.parentNode.appendChild(e)}}
if(e)e.style.display='block';Show.LastAR=e};Show.hideAR=function(){Show.LastAR.style.display='none'};Show.toggleNext=function(a){var e=a;while(e.nodeName!='DIV')e=e.nextSibling;if(!e.style){}else if(!e.style.display){}else{var d,p_;if(e.style.display=='none'){d='block';p='-'}else{d='none';p='+'}
